{
  "name": "theazo",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "description": "Theazo — AI operating infrastructure for startups and enterprises. Agent primitives (workflows, fleets, chat, RAG, MCP), sandboxed compute, multi-tenant sessions, per-user billing, observability. Bring your own compute + models or use ours.",
